e ērā atu raraunga pūtirotiro puta noa i ō pūrere kua takiurua.Ka taea e Microsoft Edge tō hītori, ō makau, kupuhipa, me ētahi atu raraunga pūtirotiro te tukutahi puta noa i ō pūrere takiuru katoa. $1Tauākī Tūmataitinga Microsoft.Kua puta he raruraru. Me mahi anō koa ā muri ake te wā poto.Hei tukutahi i ō raraunga pūtirotiro, whakakāngia te tukutahi.Ūkui makau, hītori, kupuhipa me ētahi atu raraunga tirotiro i tēnei pūrere.Mōhiohio utungaWhakakī aunoatia ngā raraunga pukaTakiuru me GoogleKei te kawemai…Me kawemai iKōtahaKōwhiria he aha hei kawemaiNgā kupuhipa kawemai o mua mō ngā pae rite ka tuhiruatiaWhārangi kāingaWhārangi whakaohoWhakatuwhera ngā ripaĀkona ētahi atu mea mō ēnei tautuhingaKua oti!Kua neke mātou i ō raraunga.Ka haere tonu te hekenga toronga i te papamuri.I rahua te kawemai i te $1.meI kawemai i ētahi tūemi anakeKa aroha, kāore e taea te kawemai i ō raraungaAko me pēhea te kaweake$1 he kōnae kupuhipa CSV mai i tētahi kaiwhakahaere kupuhipaKua kawea mai e mātou ōu kupuhipaKia haere tonu ki te tiaki i ōu kupuhipa kei roto i a Microsoft Edge, whakakāngia "$1" kei roto i Ngā TautuhingaKatia a Google Chrome i mua i te haere tonu.Kati Google Chrome kia haere tonu te kawemaiTakiputaTangohia te kōtahaHoki atu ki $1 whārangi.WhakahōuHaere ki taku pūketeWhakatika kōtahaKa hiahiatia tae atu ki te 24 haora kia mana rā anō ngā huringa.Ka mukua pūmautia tēnei i ngā raraunga tirotiro pēnei i ngā makau, hītori, me ngā kupuhipa i tēnei pūrere. Heoi anō, ko ngā raraunga i mua i te tukutahitia ki tō kōtaha, ka noho e pāhono ana ki tō pūkete Microsoft.Ka mukua pūmautia tēnei i ngā raraunga tirotiro pēnei i ngā makau, hītori, me ngā kupuhipa i tēnei pūrere.Me tango i tēnei kōtahaĒtahi kōtaha anōWhakamahinga inā tata nei (taunoa)$1 ($2)Taunoa tonu, ka whakamahia e Microsoft Edge te kōtaha whakamahi tōmuri hei whera hononga i rō īmēra me ērā atu taupānga. Mēnā he kōtaha anō āu i roto o Microsoft Edge, me kōwhiri tētahi hei whakamahi. Ka takahia tēnei tautuhinga e ngā manakohanga kōtaha mō ngā pae kua tautuhi i raro nei.Kōtaha taunoa mō ngā hononga ā-wahohttps://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2114187https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2077327Whakatika te āpure tāuru ingoa kōtahaTāpiri āpure tāuru ingoa kōtahaKei te raruraru te tukutahi raraunga tirotiro ki ō pūrere takiurua katoa. $1Tīmata anō i te tukutahi, takiputa, ka takiuru mai anō.Kia tukutahi tonu, tāurua tō kīangahipa tukutahi.Kāore Tukutahi i te wātea mō tēnei pūkete $1https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2121003Kua whakakāia e tō umanga te tukutahi mō tēnei pūrere.Ki te takiputa koe, kāore e taea tēnei wāhitau īmēra te pāhono ki tō kōtaha.Takiuru kia tukutahi ō raraunga tirotiro puta noa ō pūrereKa mukua ngā raraunga katoa i tēnei pūrere e pā ana ki tēnei wāhitau īmēra, ā, kāore e whakaoratia anō.Takiuru hei whiwhi 1,000 ngā ira Microsoft Rewards.Ka taea e koe te hoko tohu mō ngā kāri koha me ētahi atu ina e takiuru ana koe mō te papatono Microsoft Rewards.E hiahia ana ahau ki te hono ki Microsoft RewardsMā te taki i te pouaka, ka whiwhi īmēra koe mō Microsoft Rewards, arā ko ngā tono mō ngā hua Microsoft me ngā hua a ngā hoa.https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/servicesagreementWhakahaere pūketehttps://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2101140Hurihia te pikitiaWhakaotia te takiuruAta awatāKōtaha whakahōuI tangohia te pūkete i tūhono ki tēnei kōtaha, engari kei konei tonu ō raraunga tirotiro. Takiuru anō kia tūhono anō i te pūkete.E pāhono ana tēnei kōtaha ki te pūkete mahi, kura rānei i te pūrereĒtahi atu manakohanga kōtahaNgā pūkete honoaNgā pūkete e honoa ana ki tō kōtaha Microsoft EdgeMe wete i tēnei pūkete tuihono?Ka wete tēnei i te pūkete tuihono e whakamahia ana $1 mai i tēnei kōtaha.Wetehonongia te pūketeKa tae mai ākuanei! Ka whakakāia e mātou ina rite iaUru māmā, whakaraupapa, whakahaere i ō whārangi tiaki me ngā pae.Kia ngāwari noa te urua, te whakaritea, te whakahaeretia hoki ō whārangi tiaki me ngā pae, tae rā anō ki ngā ripa i waihotia e koeWhakatikaia ō taut