    takahi ngā tautuhinga Pare Taupānga i ngā tautuhinga manakohanga kōtaha Microsoft Edge.Ka kitea i konei ngā pae e kōwhiri koe hei whakawhiti aunoa i ngā kōtaha.Tāpirihia ngā manakohanga kōtaha mō ngā paeKua whakatikatia te paeexample.comKei te rārangi kē te paetukutukuKāore te hōputu paetukutuku i te tikaKei te putu te āpure paetukutukuKua mukua te paeKaua e whakawhitiwhitiTātaritia ngā paeŪkui tātariKua ūkuia te tātariKāore i kitea he hua rapu$1 te hua rapu i kitea$1 ngā hua rapu i kiteaMe tino muku rānei te pae?Rārangi paetukutuku whakawhiti kōtaha aunoa.Ngā WāhimahiKa whakatuwhera a Microsoft Edge i ngā hononga ā-waho ki te matapihi tiri-kore mutunga, ki te mokowāmahi i tīpakohia rāneiMokowāmahi taunoa mō ngā hononga ā-wahoTāpiri, whakatika me te muku i ngā paetukutuku mō ngā mokowāmahi tauwhāiti ki konei.Manakohanga mokowāmahi mō ngā hononga ā-wahoMokowāmahiKāore i a koe he manakohanga mokowāmahi hononga ā-waho. Pāwhiri i a "Tāpiri Paetukutuku" hei tāpiri i tētahi.Ripanga rārangi paetukutuku manakohanga mokowāmahiTāpiria he paetukutukuKua whakatikaKei te tīariari kē he ture mō tēnei paeHōputu paetukutuku muhu (Ngā tauira tika: abc.com, xyz.abc.com)Kaua te āpure paetukutuku e piakoMatapihi tōmuri (taunoa)Mukua ngā kōnae manakohanga mokowāmahiMēnā kei te raru koe ki te tukutahi i ngā Mokowāmahi Edge puta noa i ō pūrere takiuru, me ngana ki te tautuhi anō i te kōnae manakohanga. $1https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/deployedge/edge-learnmore-reset-data-in-cloudMukunga angituKua rahua te mukuTukutahi i te kīangahipaWhakakāia te kīangahipaKua whakamunaia e koe ō raraunga mā te kīangahipa tukutahi. Ina wareware i a koe tō kīangahipa, ina hiahia rānei tēnei te whakaweto, me tautuhi anō ō raraunga tukutahi.Mō te haumarutanga tāpiri, me whakamuna ngā raraunga tukutahi ki tāu ake kīangahipa tukutahi.Ina whakamahi kīangahipa tukutahi koe, tē taea e Microsoft te whakamahi ō raraunga tukutahi mō ngā wheako whakawhaiaro.Me ako anō mō ngā kīangahipa ritenga.He aha te kīangahipa Tukutahi, me pēhea hoki e whakamahia e au?Mā te kīangahipa Tukutahi e tāpiria e koe he kī whakamunatanga ritenga ki ō raraunga tukutahi. Kei te whakamunaia kē e Microsoft Edge ētahi raraunga, pēnei i ō kupuhipa me te raraunga whakakī aunoa, engari ka taea te hanga kīangahipa tukutahi hei apa whakamunatanga tāpiri.Ina kā mai te kīangahipa tukutahi, ka whakamuna e Microsoft Edge ō raraunga mā tō kīangahipa kia kore ai e wetemunaia ki ērā atu pūrere āu ki te kore e whakaūkia tō kīangahipa.https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=2146263Ka wātea noa te kīangahipa Tukutahi i ngā Hongere Insider. Ki te whakakā koe i tēnei, ka wetohia te tukutahi i te Hongere Stable me Microsoft Edge mō iOS me Android.Ka wātea noa te kīangahipa Tukutahi i ngā Hongere Canary me Dev. Ki te whakakā koe i tēnei, ka wetohia te tukutahi i ngā Hongere Beta, Stable me Microsoft Edge mō iOS me Android.Tāurua kīangahipa.Whakaūngia te kīangahip